-- Persimmon Says Its First-Half Sales Increase, Lifted by Higher Home Prices
-- Andrew Blackman
-- 2010-07-06T06:00:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/persimmon-says-its-first-half-sales-increase-lifted-by-higher-home-prices.html

          
          
             Persimmon Plc, the U.K.’s third-
largest homebuilder by volume, said sales in the first six
months of the year rose about 26 percent to 785 million pounds
as the housing market’s recovery enabled the company to increase
prices.  
          
          


  


        